The //Radon-norm// $$\|\cdot\|_\mathrm{RD}$$ on $$\measures(\R^d)$$ is defined as
$$
\|\gamma\|_\mathrm{RD} \coloneqq \sup_{
  \substack{g \in \smoothbd(\R^d), \\ \|g\|_\infty \le 1}
}
\left| \int_{\R^d} g \,\d\gamma \right|.
$$